*Background of Request*

Confluence user might continue their page edit or create process offsite where there are no internet connection available which lead them to lost their session unknowingly. Since Confluence unable to saved the draft without client to server connection, Confluence will automatically drop the user session and all of their work are not saved in Confluence as a draft.

It would be great if Confluence able to store the draft locally and synchronize it into Confluence server when they are back online. This way no users work will be lost in between.

